    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划与英国首相斯塔默和阿联酋领导人举行会晤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/trump-plans-meetings-with-uk-s-starmer-and-leader-of-the-uae</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位高级顾问透露，共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普计划会见英国新任首相基尔·斯塔默以及阿拉伯联合酋长国总统，因为在美国大选的阴影下，这位前总统继续在外国领导人中保持影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/trump-plans-meetings-with-uk-s-starmer-and-leader-of-the-uae</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:38:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NHK 称日本军舰首次穿越台湾海峡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/japan-warship-sails-through-taiwan-strait-in-a-first-nhk-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NHK 援引不愿透露姓名的知情人士的话称，日本海上自卫队军舰周三首次穿越台湾海峡。]]></description>
