    <item>
      <title>纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯在联邦腐败调查后被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nyc-mayor-adams-indicted-after-federal-corruption-probe-nyt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，纽约市市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）在接受联邦腐败调查后已被起诉，这一令人震惊的进展让人们对这位美国最大城市的负责人的政治前途产生了怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nyc-mayor-adams-indicted-after-federal-corruption-probe-nyt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国赞扬中国提前获悉洲际弹道导弹试验以避免误判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/us-hails-china-s-advanced-notice-of-icbm-test-as-good-thing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼称赞中国在太平洋试射洲际弹道导弹之前的透明度，这表明两个超级大国之间的军事交流正在改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/us-hails-china-s-advanced-notice-of-icbm-test-as-good-thing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 00:39:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称，保持美国钢铁国内生产比就业“最重要”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/harris-says-keeping-us-steel-domestic-worth-threatened-job-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党总统候选人卡马拉·哈里斯表示，如果日本新日铁公司收购美国钢铁公司的交易失败，保持国内对钢铁生产的控制比可能出现的失业更为重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/harris-says-keeping-us-steel-domestic-worth-threatened-job-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 00:04:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国、澳大利亚计划签署防御条约以加速 Aukus 潜艇交付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/uk-australia-plan-defense-treaty-to-speed-aukus-subs-delivery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在澳大利亚和英国于伦敦举行会谈之前，两国宣布将致力于达成一项双边防御条约，旨在加快部署下一代核动力潜艇舰队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/uk-australia-plan-defense-treaty-to-speed-aukus-subs-delivery</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:23:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯计划访问亚利桑那州边境以解决移民问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/kamala-harris-to-visit-us-mexico-border-confronting-immigration-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将于周五访问美墨边境，试图向选民表明她对移民和边境安全问题有着坚定的把握，这是11月大选的一个关键政策关注点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/kamala-harris-to-visit-us-mexico-border-confronting-immigration-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登会见越南领导人，加强美国在亚洲的联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/biden-meets-vietnam-s-top-leader-in-veiled-counter-china-play</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国努力对抗中国在亚洲的经济和安全影响力之际，总统乔·拜登会见了越南共产党总书记苏林，庆祝与越南“关系进入新时代”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/biden-meets-vietnam-s-top-leader-in-veiled-counter-china-play</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国、欧洲和盟国提出停火计划以避免黎巴嫩战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-working-with-allies-to-halt-israel-hezbollah-war-in-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国、欧洲盟友和阿拉伯国家提议以色列和黎巴嫩真主党之间停火三周，为谈判铺平道路，避免在以色列军队连日空袭后爆发全面战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-working-with-allies-to-halt-israel-hezbollah-war-in-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 17:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
